<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-59907" src="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ali-wakili1-1.jpg" alt="" width="492" height="402" srcset="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ali-wakili1-1.jpg 492w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ali-wakili1-1-150x123.jpg 150w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ali-wakili1-1-420x343.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px" /> Senator Ali Wakili, representing the Southern Senatorial zone of Bauchi state is dead. It was reported that he slumped and died in his residence in Abuja on Saturday. Wakili died at the age of 58. Senate President Bukola Sarki expressed his sympathy to the family and prayed for the soul of the departed in tweet on Saturday .   